message.body: Hi! I left my last partner hanging so Ill start this one off right in an attempt to redeem myself. Waddap?
Haha, you're off to a great.start. Im on my 15minute break at work. And you?
Making a deposit on a new apartment! Such fun...
That's really exiting! New place means house warming party. And all that really means is that you get free stuff!
Thats a good thought - I think all my friends are pretty poor so theyll probably just bring guacomole... but Ill take it! My last chat partner was a ling
uistics grad student so I think she was secretly helping run this program. Are you as well?
Never say no to free guac. And no, I'm,not helping run the program. Im a poor college student working a dead end minimum wage job
Been there! What are you studying? I finished undergrad in 2008 and been working as a videomeister since.
Anthro. Im going to end up living in a tent somewhere near the Sahara poor and dirty but happy.
I need to find an internship that pays.
